{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01RvGc9frGztnRJMjnbBQRrG","type":"tool_result","content":"     1â†’# Cloche MVP Implementation Plan\n     2â†’\n     3â†’> **For Claude:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task.\n     4â†’\n     5â†’**Goal:** Build a working Cloche MVP â€” parse workflow DSL, execute steps in Docker containers, report status via gRPC.\n     6â†’\n     7â†’**Architecture:** Three Go binaries (cloche, cloched, cloche-agent) with hexagonal architecture. Domain types and DSL parser are the foundation. Build bottom-up: domain -> DSL -> engine -> agent binary -> daemon -> CLI.\n     8â†’\n     9â†’**Tech Stack:** Go 1.22+, protobuf/gRPC, Docker SDK, SQLite (via modernc.org/sqlite â€” pure Go), testify for assertions.\n    10â†’\n    11â†’---\n    12â†’\n    13â†’## Phase 1: Foundation\n    14â†’\n    15â†’### Task 1: Initialize Go Module and Directory Structure\n    16â†’\n    17â†’**Files:**\n    18â†’- Create: `go.mod`\n    19â†’- Create: `Makefile`\n    20â†’- Create: `cmd/cloche/main.go`\n    21â†’- Create: `cmd/cloched/main.go`\n    22â†’- Create: `cmd/cloche-agent/main.go`\n    23â†’\n    24â†’**Step 1: Initialize Go module**\n    25â†’\n    26â†’```bash\n    27â†’cd /home/lucas/workspace/cloche\n    28â†’go mod init github.com/cloche-dev/cloche\n    29â†’```\n    30â†’\n    31â†’**Step 2: Create directory structure**\n    32â†’\n    33â†’```bash\n    34â†’mkdir -p cmd/cloche cmd/cloched cmd/cloche-agent\n    35â†’mkdir -p internal/domain internal/ports\n    36â†’mkdir -p internal/adapters/docker internal/adapters/sqlite\n    37â†’mkdir -p internal/adapters/grpc internal/adapters/agents/generic\n    38â†’mkdir -p internal/adapters/agents/claudecode\n    39â†’mkdir -p internal/dsl internal/engine internal/protocol\n    40â†’```\n    41â†’\n    42â†’**Step 3: Create placeholder mains**\n    43â†’\n    44â†’`cmd/cloche/main.go`:\n    45â†’```go\n    46â†’package main\n    47â†’\n    48â†’func main() {}\n    49â†’```\n    50â†’\n    51â†’`cmd/cloched/main.go`:\n    52â†’```go\n    53â†’package main\n    54â†’\n    55â†’func main() {}\n    56â†’```\n    57â†’\n    58â†’`cmd/cloche-agent/main.go`:\n    59â†’```go\n    60â†’package main\n    61â†’\n    62â†’func main() {}\n    63â†’```\n    64â†’\n    65â†’**Step 4: Create Makefile**\n    66â†’\n    67â†’```makefile\n    68â†’.PHONY: build test lint clean\n    69â†’\n    70â†’build:\n    71â†’\tgo build -o bin/cloche ./cmd/cloche\n    72â†’\tgo build -o bin/cloched ./cmd/cloched\n    73â†’\tgo build -o bin/cloche-agent ./cmd/cloche-agent\n    74â†’\n    75â†’test:\n    76â†’\tgo test ./... -v\n    77â†’\n    78â†’test-short:\n    79â†’\tgo test ./... -short\n    80â†’\n    81â†’lint:\n    82â†’\tgo vet ./...\n    83â†’\n    84â†’clean:\n    85â†’\trm -rf bin/\n    86â†’```\n    87â†’\n    88â†’**Step 5: Verify build**\n    89â†’\n    90â†’```bash\n    91â†’make build\n    92â†’```\n    93â†’Expected: three binaries in `bin/`\n    94â†’\n    95â†’**Step 6: Commit**\n    96â†’\n    97â†’```bash\n    98â†’git add -A && git commit -m \"feat: initialize Go module and project structure\"\n    99â†’```\n   100â†’"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_014nB1uYcqdGQDnmCdayJAtm","session_id":"4d7e8ba7-70ae-45e4-b438-c668f354765a","uuid":"0058c47a-0859-44d8-afb5-392dab66d9ff"}
