{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Y2WNnoei5642v3ez3uuwns","type":"tool_result","content":"     1â†’# Project Settings File: config.toml\n     2â†’\n     3â†’**Date:** 2026-03-06\n     4â†’**Status:** Design\n     5â†’\n     6â†’## Problem\n     7â†’\n     8â†’The per-project settings file is `.cloche/config` with no extension, making it\n     9â†’ambiguous and inconsistent with the TOML library in use.\n    10â†’\n    11â†’## Change\n    12â†’\n    13â†’Rename to `.cloche/config.toml`. No backwards compatibility with the old filename.\n    14â†’\n    15â†’## Default file (created by `cloche init`)\n    16â†’\n    17â†’```toml\n    18â†’# Cloche project configuration\n    19â†’\n    20â†’[orchestration]\n    21â†’concurrency        = 1\n    22â†’stagger_seconds    = 1.0\n    23â†’# list_tasks_command = \"bash .cloche/scripts/ready-tasks.sh\"\n    24â†’# dedup_seconds    = 300\n    25â†’\n    26â†’[evolution]\n    27â†’enabled           = true\n    28â†’debounce_seconds  = 30\n    29â†’min_confidence    = \"medium\"\n    30â†’max_prompt_bullets = 50\n    31â†’```\n    32â†’\n    33â†’Notes:\n    34â†’- `orchestration.concurrency` defaults to `1` (single run at a time).\n    35â†’- `orchestration.stagger_seconds` adds delay between consecutive launches (default `1.0`).\n    36â†’- `orchestration.list_tasks_command` (optional) is a shell command that outputs a JSON array of\n    37â†’  task objects (`[{\"id\":\"...\",\"title\":\"...\",\"description\":\"...\"}]`). When set, the daemon\n    38â†’  picks tasks and passes the ID via `CLOCHE_TASK_ID` env var.\n    39â†’- `orchestration.dedup_seconds` (default `300`) prevents reassignment of the same task ID\n    40â†’  within the timeout window.\n    41â†’- Commented-out keys show optional overrides that rarely need changing.\n    42â†’\n    43â†’## Code changes\n    44â†’\n    45â†’| File | Change |\n    46â†’|------|--------|\n    47â†’| `internal/config/config.go` | `Load()`: change path from `\"config\"` to `\"config.toml\"` |\n    48â†’| `cmd/cloche/init.go` | Add `config.toml` to the files created by init |\n    49â†’| `.cloche/config` (existing file in this repo) | Rename to `.cloche/config.toml` |\n    50â†’"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_014nB1uYcqdGQDnmCdayJAtm","session_id":"4d7e8ba7-70ae-45e4-b438-c668f354765a","uuid":"bdec0133-fbc0-4628-8874-a5235e2e2236"}
